1 effective date of this section whose terms are set to expire in 2029 shall be extended by one year.
2 Regular municipal elections in the Town of Brookford shall resume in even-numbered years
3 beginning in 2028 with the same staggering of terms as when elections were conducted in the
4 odd-numbered years.
