7 SECTION 3.(b) No municipal elections shall be conducted in the City of Claremont
8 in 2027. The terms of office for the three council members in the City of Claremont serving on
9 the effective date of this section whose terms are set to expire in 2027 shall be extended by one
10 year. The terms of office for the mayor and two council members in the City of Claremont serving
11 on the effective date of this section whose terms are set to expire in 2029 shall be extended by
12 one year. Regular municipal elections in the City of Claremont shall resume in even-numbered
13 years beginning in 2028 with the same staggering of terms as when elections were conducted in
14 the odd-numbered years.
