4 "Section 3.2. Manner of Election of Board. Council. The qualified voters of the entire
5 City elect the members of the Board.Council.
6 "Section 3.3. Term of Office of Members of the Board. Council. Members of the Board
7 Council are elected to four-year staggered terms. In 1991 and each four years thereafter, three
8 members of the Board shall be elected. In 1993 and each four years thereafter, three members of
9 the Board shall be elected.
10 "Section 3.4. Election of Mayor; Term of Office. The qualified voters of the entire City
11 elect the Mayor. A new Mayor shall be elected in 1991 and each two years thereafter.Mayor who
12 shall serve a four-year term."
